data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN LESS THAN CURRENT INTEREST RATE, ASK YOUR RELATOR ABOUT IT TODAY.     Nestled in the heart of Arroyo Grande's highly sought-after Berry Gardens neighborhood, 1550 Strawberry is a captivating single-level residence offering 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and an enticing BONUS room (not included in the square footage).    Upon crossing the threshold, you'll be welcomed by an inviting open floor plan seamlessly connecting the elegant formal living room, a gourmet chef's kitchen, a delightful dining area, and a cozy family room.    As you explore further, the master suite beckons on your right, boasting a generously sized bedroom, a capacious walk-in closet, and an opulent ensuite bathroom featuring a private toilet area, dual vanity sinks, a standalone shower, and a luxurious soaking tub.    Two additional well-appointed guest bedrooms, each adorned with ample closet space, share a tastefully designed guest bathroom.    A unique feature of this remarkable home is the transformation of the two-car garage into a commodious living quarters, adding flexibility to your living space options.    Step outside to discover an expansive patio area where you can unwind in the soothing embrace of a jacuzzi or savor outdoor moments by the BBQ.    Don't let the opportunity slip through your fingers to own this enchanting Berry Gardens residence, promising a serene residential ambiance while keeping you conveniently proximate to local schools, verdant parks, diverse shopping destinations, delectable dining options, and the picturesque beach.
